               format.   The   idea  is  that   you  can   avoid  manual
               preparation of certain portions of your  manuscript (such
               as the  table of  contents and the  index) by  making PUB
               prepare them mechanically.

               The generated file of a portion may remain empty,  or may
               be  written on  during  the processing  of  portions that
               appear  earlier  in  the  manuscript.   For  example, the
                                  7.9        CONTENTS and  PORTION INDEX               generated files  for PORTION
