               generated file for  the named portion.  The  portion must
               appear  later  in  the  manuscript.   Before  sending the
               template, the  compiler substitutes for  every occurrence
               of:
{ <v> }

               the (unquoted) value of the variable <v>.

               Thus, if S=6 and PAGE=26, then the statement:

.SEND CONTENTS $(
Section {S} -- Findings ^N.^Y {PAGE}
.)$ ;
